			<h2 class="story">
				

				

				
				<span id="title-70407747"> <a onclick="return toggle_fh_body_wrap_return(this);"  href="//yro.slashdot.org/story/15/02/19/2012203/darkleaks-an-online-black-market-for-selling-secrets">Darkleaks: an Online Black Market For Selling Secrets</a></span>
				
				
				<span class="comments commentcnt-70407747" >21</span>
				

				
			</h2>
