			<h2 class="story">
				

				

				
				<span id="title-70390117"> <a onclick="return toggle_fh_body_wrap_return(this);"  href="//science.slashdot.org/story/15/02/19/0317252/could-fossils-of-ancient-life-from-earth-reside-on-the-moon">Could Fossils of Ancient Life From Earth Reside On the Moon?</a></span>
				
				
